{"tid":1070854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13碎囝為狗狗報仇，初弒親母！","createTime":"2019-03-21T03:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T14:13:24.000Z","uid":202464,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5931fd59ab0f263ab345184d5f541f90593d90bd","tid":1070854,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"中國江蘇省日前發生<span style=\"color: red;\">一起弒母兇殺案</span>，一名13歲的邵姓男童手持菜刀活活砍死母親，事發後隨即<span style=\"color: red;\">進行逃逸</span>，18日有人發現邵母遺體報警處理<span style=\"color: red;\">，整起</span>案件才因此曝光。<br />\n<br />\n最新案情曝光，事發原因竟是邵母當場摔死男童的愛犬，他才會殺了媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n鄰居透露，楊女因為兒子整天都和狗狗玩，成績一路往下掉，當天雙方發生嚴重衝突，楊女威脅打死小狗，男童則嗆「打死小狗我就殺了妳」，結果小狗死了，楊女也真的被男童殺死了。"},{"pid":"53773ffadd329a3bfcf6428cebbb642cd1d614c3","tid":1070854,"uid":44454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"好呀，做人要有口齒"},{"pid":"630e1528757f85b2de68e4540efb04e9f3053c6b","tid":1070854,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蝗。初弒</span>"},{"pid":"a94486e8a18957f414b45906805b70ae21cf7a92","tid":1070854,"uid":140580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"會打死隻狗，個呀媽都唔係好人"},{"pid":"177fef4576a2101737e72d08b038505038c28b63","tid":1070854,"uid":237417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"必成大器"},{"pid":"6b4b1b022bb5f3c5e05374efb00130cd5c4c876a","tid":1070854,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a94486e8a18957f414b45906805b70ae21cf7a92","tid":1070854,"uid":140580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"會打死隻狗，個呀媽都唔係好人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"個仔都只係似老母"},{"pid":"c0914e69e5a77480448f59ff7a8eac4c5365c692","tid":1070854,"uid":57802,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"John wick"},{"pid"